query:
SELECT 
  sc.id as checkId,
  sc.customerOrderNumber,
  sc.status,
  sci.productSku,
  sci.productName,
  sci.expectedQuantity,
  sci.checkedQuantity,
  sci.divergence,
  sc.createdAt
FROM stageChecks sc
LEFT JOIN stageCheckItems sci ON sc.id = sci.stageCheckId
WHERE sc.status IN ('divergent', 'in_progress')
ORDER BY sc.id DESC
LIMIT 10;
